 fan-out (count N for `native` executor) runs N sequential `@deep-research` agent dispatches with isolated dirs. CLI fan-out runs N headless subprocesses concurrently in the capped pool.\n\n  Line 259:    |     (repeatable; each occurrence adds one entry to config.fanout.executors)\n\n  Line 260:    |-- --executors=<json> -> config.fanout.executors = parse(json) escape hatch for complex configs\n\n  Line 261:    |-- --concurrency=N -> config.fanout.concurrency (default 2)\n\n  Line 265:    |   - 2+ --executor flags, --executors, or any count>1: write config.fanout\n\n  Line 290:    - memory_context({ input: research_topic OR \"deep-research\", mode: \"focused\", includeContent: true })\n\n  Line 370:   - \"fanout_executors\"\n\n  Line 371:   - \"fanout_concurrency\"\n\n  Line 454:   - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 455:   - \"memory_search\"\n\n  Line 467:     - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 468:     - \"memory_search\"\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_ai-council.contract.md:\n  Line 217:     - scope_extract\n\n  Line 344:    - memory_context({ input: deliberation_topic OR \"deep-ai-council\", mode: \"focused\", includeContent: true })\n\n  Line 359:      A) Autonomous - run setup, topic loops, synthesis, and save without approval\n\n  Line 360:      B) Interactive - pause at setup, loop, synthesis, and save gates\n\n  Line 524:   - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 525:   - \"memory_search\"\n\n  Line 537:     - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 538:     - \"memory_search\"\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/assets/compiled/deep_alignment.contract.md:\n  Line 139:     - scope_extract\n\n  Line 158: 2. **Tier 2 — Resolve lanes** (the one input that is never guessed): when `--lane-config` is absent, emit ONLY the structured three-axis scoping question (`authority` x `artifactClass` x `scope`) from `.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-al