anout_executors` | N | repeatable `--executor=<type>` flags or `--executors=<json>`; each group accepts `--model`, `--config-dir`, `--reasoning-effort`, `--service-tier`, `--executor-timeout`, `--iters`, `--label`, `--count` | none (single-executor when absent) | N |\n\n  Line 227: | `fanout_concurrency` | N | flag `--concurrency=N` | `2` | N |\n\n  Line 229: **Fan-out default policy:** 0–1 `--executor` flags and no `--executors` → `config.executor` (single-executor, default, unchanged). 2+ `--executor` flags, `--executors`, or any `--count > 1` → `config.fanout`. Review fan-out uses strongest-restriction: any lineage active P0 → merged FAIL. Native and CLI fan-out lineages run under `fanout-run.cjs` in the capped pool so every lineage shares retries, artifact checks, and stop-policy validation. The native adapter calls the `deep/review` command with the internal `--fanout-lineage-artifact-dir` override; it must not dispatch the LEAF `@deep-review` agent or a pasted phase-running prompt as a full-loop sub-agent. When fan-out includes `cli-opencode`, that lineage is an explicit parallel-detached OpenCode session with its own lineage directory and session id; this is the documented exception to the cli-opencode self-invocation guard. Single-executor `cli-opencode` remains cross-runtime only.\n\n  Line 277:    |-- --fanout-lineage-artifact-dir=PATH -> config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir = PATH (internal single-lineage command invocation only)\n\n  Line 279:    |     (repeatable; each occurrence adds one entry to config.fanout.executors)\n\n  Line 280:    |-- --executors=<json> -> config.fanout.executors = parse(json) escape hatch\n\n  Line 281:    |-- --concurrency=N -> config.fanout.concurrency (default 2)\n\n  Line 285:    |   - 2+ --executor flags, --executors, or any count>1: write config.fanout\n\n  Line 311:    - memory_context({ input: review_target OR \"deep-review\", mode: \"focused\", includeContent: true })\n\n  Line 386: - `config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir` when present\n\n  Line 413:   - \"config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir\"\n\n  Line 414:   - \"fanout_executors\"\n\n  Line 415:   - \"fanout_concurrency\"\n\n  Line 495:   - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 496:   - \"memory_search\"\n\n  Line 507:     - \"memory_context\"\n\n  Line 508:     - \"memory_search\"\n","metadata":{"matches":56,"truncated":false},"title":"scope|fanout|spec.md|stage_artifact|save|memory","time":{"start":1784377927319,"end":1784377927329}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0a81daa3e07133d1016a5b7246b8648191a110aefa56a949fc"}},"id":"prt_f753665e8001hnciwKQi8v5oOT","sessionID":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","messageID":"msg_f75362e79001lnsHyfw5uCC7ez"}}
