ence.\n+\n+## OUTPUT CONTRACT\n+\n+Produce the three canonical iteration artifacts. The state and delta iteration records must be identical and include `type:\"iteration\"`, `iteration:2`, `run:2`, mode/route proof, novelty fields, status/focus/counts, exact key/answered question arrays, ruled-out directions, sources, timestamp, lineage fields, and executor `{kind:\"cli-opencode\",model:\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\",reasoningEffort:null,serviceTier:null}`. The narrative must include Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Questions Answered, Questions Remaining, Dead Ends, Assessment, Reflection, Sources Consulted, and Recommended Next Focus.\n+\n+Answer the combined audit/Open Design key question only if both modes receive a complete operational contract and ship-order recommendation.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,44 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_s