{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784378977390,"sessionID":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_xrsaUbDw4rMKXQZI2j79gOX5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Research audit transport integration","subagent_type":"deep-research","command":"/deep:research:auto","prompt":"Execute exactly ONE deep-research LEAF iteration. This is research with required artifact writes, not implementation. Read and follow the complete prompt pack at `.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-2.md`. Read state first. Use no subagents and no nested loops. Write only the three allowed iteration artifacts named in that prompt, and verify all three exist and satisfy its route-proof schema before returning. Do not modify any other path."},"output":"<task id=\"ses_08abeb751ffe7gMt1b76J0YZ4c\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Iteration 2 Complete\n\n**Focus**: Audit comparison evidence and Open Design transport grounding  \n**Findings**: 6 findings (5 new, 1 partially new)  \n**newInfoRatio**: 0.92  \n**Questions answered**: Combined design-audit/Open Design question  \n**Questions remaining**: 3  \n**Edge cases**: None  \n**Recommended next focus**: `design-interface` relational exemplar contract\n\n**Files written**:\n- `research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-002.md`\n- `research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl` — exactly one record appended\n- `research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-002.jsonl`\n\n**Verification**:\n- All three artifacts exist: yes\n- JSONL append count: 1\n- State/delta records identical: yes\n- Route proof and executor schema valid: yes\n- Exact question arrays valid: yes\n- Findings citations complete: yes\n- Packet boundary respected: yes\n- Reducer-owned files untouched: yes\n- Subagents used: no\n\n**Status**: complete\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","sess