{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784379050854,"sessionID":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_uQymz00lXdVrrXiVY6ES5mIR","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 3\n+\n+## STATE\n+\n+Segment: 1 | Iteration: 3 of 10\n+Questions: reducer shows 1/5 answered; iteration evidence has substantively answered the hub and audit/Open Design questions.\n+Last ratios: 0.83 -> 0.92 | Stuck count: 0\n+Next focus: How should design-interface use coherent style exemplars for grounding, anti-default critique, variation diversity, and handoff without becoming a chooser or copy path?\n+\n+## REQUIRED ACTIONS\n+\n+1. Read state, strategy, registry, iterations 1-2, and phase-001 synthesis first.\n+2. Inspect interface's register/dials, context-loading, design principles, variation-diversity, real-UI, preflight, redesign, transform, and sk-code handoff contracts selectively.\n+3. Validate a relational exemplar flow against 2-3 contrasting real corpus bundles already identified by phase 001 (for example Kobu and 19-86), preserving coherent identity and provenance.\n+4. Specify exact integration points, fields, anti-copy/refusal rules, failure/fallback behavior, proof, and rough build cost.\n+5. Generate and test smart ideas beyond candidate cards/hydration, such as counterfactual critique, named default/rejected exemplar, distance budget, controlled variation seeds, and source-aware handoff locks.\n+\n+## STATE FILES\n+\n+- Config: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-config.json\n+- State Log: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-state.jsonl\n+- Strategy: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md\n+- Registry: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json\n+- Narrative output: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-003.md\n+- Delta output: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-003.jsonl\n+\n+## CONSTRAINTS\n+\n+- LEAF only; 3-5 actions; at most 12 tool calls; no subagents/nested loops.\n+- Write only the three allowed iteration outputs.\n+- Interface remains the taste authority. Corpus references are critique-ground, not presets or a chooser.\n+- One coherent anchor by default. Do not average tokens, combine signature motifs, or infer reuse rights.\n+- md-generator excluded. Cite all findings with repository file/line evidence and label inference.\n+\n+## OUTPUT CONTRACT\n+\n+Produce the three canonical artifacts. The state/delta first records must be identical canonical iteration records for iteration/run 3 with route proof, novelty, status, focus, counts, exact question arrays, ruled-out directions, sources, lineage fields, timestamp, and executor `{kind:\"cli-opencode\",model:\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\",reasoningEffort:null,serviceTier:null}`.\n+\n+If evidence fully closes it, put this exact string in `answeredQuestions`: `How should \\`design-interface\\` use coherent style exemplars for grounding, anti-default critique, variation diversity, and handoff without becoming a style chooser or copy path?`\n+\n+The narrative needs Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Questions Answered, Questions Remaining, Dead Ends, Assessment, Reflection, Sources Consulted, and Recommended Next Focus.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,44 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 3\n+\n+## STATE\n+\n+Segment: 1 | Iteration: 3 of 10\n+Questions: reducer shows 1/5 answered; iteration evidence has substantively answered the hub and audit/Open Design questions.\n+Last ratios: 0.83 -> 0.92 | Stuck count: 0\n+Next focus: How should design-interface use coherent style exemplars for grounding, anti-default critique, variation diversity, and handoff without becoming a chooser or copy path?\n+\n+## REQUIRED ACTIONS\n+\n+1. Read state, strategy, registry, iterations 1-2, and phase-001 synthesis first.\n+2. Inspect interface's register/dials, context-loading, design principles, variation-diversity, real-UI, preflight, redesign, transform, and sk-code handoff contracts selectively.\n+3. Validate a relational exemplar flow against 2-3 contrasting real corpus bundles already identified by phase