code/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-003.jsonl\n+\n+## CONSTRAINTS\n+\n+- LEAF only; 3-5 actions; at most 12 tool calls; no subagents/nested loops.\n+- Write only the three allowed iteration outputs.\n+- Interface remains the taste authority. Corpus references are critique-ground, not presets or a chooser.\n+- One coherent anchor by default. Do not average tokens, combine signature motifs, or infer reuse rights.\n+- md-generator excluded. Cite all findings with repository file/line evidence and label inference.\n+\n+## OUTPUT CONTRACT\n+\n+Produce the three canonical artifacts. The state/delta first records must be identical canonical iteration records for iteration/run 3 with route proof, novelty, status, focus, counts, exact question arrays, ruled-out directions, sources, lineage fields, timestamp, and executor `{kind:\"cli-opencode\",model:\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\",reasoningEffort:null,serviceTier:null}`.\n+\n+If evidence fully closes it, put this exact string in `answeredQuestions`: `How should \\`design-interface\\` use coherent style exemplars for grounding, anti-default critique, variation diversity, and handoff without becoming a style chooser or copy path?`\n+\n+The narrative needs Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Questions Answered, Questions Remaining, Dead Ends, Assessment, Reflection, Sources Consulted, and Recommended Next Focus.\n","additions":44,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-3.md","time":{"start":1784379050850,"end":1784379050853}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0147bc2f2b38547d016a5b7699f5608191b968380abc5e49ba"}},"id":"prt_f7547497f001dh2lVv2XIH1e1m","sessionID":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","messageID":"msg_f75472157001b1Qmg8tByZqZ0E"}}
