egy: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deep-research-strategy.md\n+- Registry: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/findings-registry.json\n+- Narrative output: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/iterations/iteration-006.md\n+- Delta output: .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/deltas/iter-006.jsonl\n+\n+## CONSTRAINTS\n+\n+- LEAF only; 3-5 actions; max 12 tool calls; no subagents/nested loops.\n+- Write only the three canonical iteration artifacts.\n+- Run the motion restraint gate conceptually before corpus retrieval. High-frequency, keyboard-driven, purposeless, or reduced-motion-unsafe behavior stays instant.\n+- Static similarity and incidental temporal vocabulary are not motion evidence. Corpus evidence cannot prove performance or accessibility.\n+- Do not copy source-specific timings or signature choreography without target reason and rights evidence.\n+- md-generator excluded. Cite every finding and label inference.\n+\n+## OUTPUT CONTRACT\n+\n+Produce canonical artifacts for iteration/run 6 with identical state/delta iteration records, route proof, novelty, focus/status/counts, exact question arrays, ruled-out directions, sources, timestamp, session/generation, and executor `{kind:\"cli-opencode\",model:\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\",reasoningEffort:null,serviceTier:null}`.\n+\n+If fully closed, `answeredQuestions` MUST contain exactly: `How should \\`design-motion\\` discover and use sparse temporal evidence, infer no motion from static styles safely, and build motion-specific exemplars or negative baselines under its restraint gate?`\n+\n+Include all standard narrative sections. Because all key questions may then be answered, recommend a synthesis-readiness/quality-guard closure pass rather than immediate implementation.\n","additions":47,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/011-sk-design-styles-utilization/003-global-modes-utilization/research/lineages/sol/prompts/iteration-6.md","time":{"start":1784380440381,"end":1784380440388}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_01d153cc10665227016a5b7c0266608191b4e47ddfa70c6f71"}},"id":"prt_f755c6987001vUD6Lg5S8A0W8H","sessionID":"ses_08acc7a6affeS35KntG0P1wx2Z","messageID":"msg_f755c44a000166jo1T61ogG9ej"}}
